description:
Description :
        Faced with doomsday, the special power inside Ling Mo was woken up. He found out that he could control zombies. Therefore, he could walk through the zombie crowd safe and sound using his power, and eventually he met his beloved girlfriend — Ye Lian, but only to find out that she has already been transformed into a zombie. To help Ye retrieve her memories, Ling Mo started his survival in doomsday.
